================
description
================

1) This program accept file name and permission from user and check whether file has given permission or not.
2) Required filename will be taken from command line

================
about the code
================

	input	:	file name, file_permission	[for more, see NOTES]
	output	:	result for permission
 			
=============
How to run
=============

	make	:	compile the code and generates executable file as "myexe"
	make run:	run the executable with command line argument
			for this you have to pass parameter as: 
			
			$ make run p1="parameter_value1" p2="parameter_value2"
	
=============
NOTES
=============

	1) file_permission : it could be-
				   i)	read
				   ii)	write
				   iii)	execute

	2)If the given file is unable to open, it will display the appropriate reason.
	
